{"tid":2020474,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★股神巴菲特 繼將航空股沽出外，亦減持了銀行股、保險股及能源企業","createTime":"2020-05-17T05:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T11:25:42.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9c33cff902e229b52724acf30a3e32f5f7f78342","tid":2020474,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:48:45.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎衝擊環球經濟，並導致股市出現大動盪，有股神之稱的資深投資者巴菲特主理的巴郡，亦調整投資組合，繼將航空股悉數沽出外，亦將減持了銀行股，及將保險股Travelers及能源企業Philips 66持股悉數沽清。<br />\n<br />\n據公告顯示，巴郡持有的高盛股權減少84%，價值由28億元（美元‧下同）降至3億元，同時將價值2,500萬元的Philips 66，及價值4,300萬元的Travelers股份悉數沽出。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，受到市價變動，資產組合減少27%，由去年底的2,420億元降至1,760億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/473856/%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%B4%E8%8F%B2%E7%89%B9%E6%B8%9B%E6%8C%81%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E4%BB%B2%E6%B2%BD%E6%B8%85%E5%91%A2%E5%85%A9%E9%9A%BB%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F473856%2F%25E8%2582%25A1%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%258F%25B2%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%259B%259B-%25E4%25BB%25B2%25E6%25B2%25BD%25E6%25B8%2585%25E5%2591%25A2%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%259A%25BB%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%2582%25A1&d=5MMtl3Q8rD8%2FKomM%2B8e611EyhmTkDJ%2BTCVbHNRNdZc8%3D&h=f179257b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/473856/%E8%82%A1%E7%A5%9E%E5%B7%B4%E8%8F%B2%E7%89%B9%E6%B8%9B%E6%8C%81%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B-%E4%BB%B2%E6%B2%BD%E6%B8%85%E5%91%A2%E5%85%A9%E9%9A%BB%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1</a>"},{"pid":"eb6468d9b0a90f34f9619d1eadcdc0d4df297cea","tid":2020474,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T05:49:34.000Z","msg":"死廢老原來裸泳左幾十年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aef4c069542a3f0c07cbb1500b932f2b6733232","tid":2020474,"uid"